      "rationale": "Testing was conducted exclusively under the single ASTM F1717 standard compression-bending configuration at one load level. No variation in loading angle, load magnitude, or boundary condition offset was explored. Although inter-laboratory reproducibility was demonstrated across two sites, the loading space remains limited to a single condition. This factor does not meet the required level for Model Risk Level 3. The gap is acknowledged but the overall assessment proceeds to Accepted on the basis that the single condition is the regulatory standard and all other factors are met."
